      "writtenOn": "2020-09-17T05:35:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Currently WiringServer implements both gRPC server and HTTP server. It\u0027s nicer if a single component (type) focuses on a single goal. For this, I recommend moving the HTTP server to another type.\n\nFor example:\n\n* WiringServer\n    * owns cacheServer\n    * implements gRPC methods\n    * maintains operations map\n    * not aware of how cached files are served\n* cacheServer\n    * implements the HTTP handler\n    * maintains cached file map\n    * not aware of operations",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 83,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 83,
        "endChar": 17
      },
      "revId": "f8427054431f6a8dddda9864ce7a8f41251753fc",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
